Effective Date: 8/15/25

The Supernova Roku App is a custom version of the Jellyfin Roku client, designed to connect to your self-hosted Jellyfin media server.

1. Information We Collect

This app does not collect or store any personal data.

All information (such as your media library, user profiles, and viewing history) is stored locally on your own Jellyfin server.

2. How We Use Your Information

No data is sent to us, the developer.

All data transfer occurs directly between your Roku device and your Jellyfin server.

3. Third-Party Services

This app does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

4. Security

The security of your data depends on your own server configuration, network setup, and password management.

We recommend enabling HTTPS on your Jellyfin server and keeping your Roku device updated.

5. Changes to This Policy

If this Privacy Policy changes, we will update the Effective Date at the top of this page.

6. Contact

For privacy-related questions, contact:
